    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting unblemished exterior aesthetics and a pristine interior cabin. Meticulously serviced and rigorously inspected, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking uncompromising mechanical integrity and a sophisticated driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
